{"in": {"title": "Ode to an iPhone", "subtitle": "by katya raman, 2018", "lines": ["NARRATOR: O sacred golden iPhone in my hand,", "NARRATOR: O Portal to dimensions yet unknown:", "NARRATOR: These thoughts I'm sent like scribbles scrawled on sand,", "NARRATOR: On distant shores where stormy winds have blown,", "NARRATOR: Would all have died before my willing ears,", "NARRATOR: Could listen patiently to empathize,", "NARRATOR: With every concern - all your deepest fears,", "NARRATOR: To share those teardrops from your limpid eyes.", "NARRATOR: But by this magic, many miles away,", "NARRATOR: I cross the seven seas to be with you,", "NARRATOR: And we, together, just like yesterday,", "NARRATOR: Will brave your trying times to see them through,", "NARRATOR: Gone, the day when no one's nearby.", "NARRATOR: Gone, the lonely laugh, the silent cry."], "speaker_map": {"NARRATOR": "Joanna", "SCENE": "Matthew", "TITLE": "Joanna", "SMALL VOICE": "Raveena", "FANGS": "Brian", "PEONY": "Raveena"}}, "out": {"cache_id": "3202a19a4f7215a39ada366e55273c1c", "audio_objects": [["73421d74bca9e982d365f81faed2a063-o-sacred-golden-iphone-in---", 0], ["751b3e13b2a7ceb8eecc124c18b5fc15-o-portal-to-dimensions-ye---", 0], ["92c7e495238c30734ab3fea3b7983864-these-thoughts-i-m-sent-l---", 0], ["614295950943a4bd1281f65addf47a00-on-distant-shores-where-s---", 0], ["046958adc8fae8a142ca2aa339658ceb-would-all-have-died-befor---", 0], ["6aa2fbb2a71f216cafdb6cfded07706a-could-listen-patiently-to---", 0], ["0bdd7e91ee7bea348ae57a29e35d0ec7-with-every-concern---all----", 0], ["6f428c222c56a5121cb2234e1aa750e1-to-share-those-teardrops----", 0], ["614f4caf9915c9169d5d61c848fbe418-but-by-this-magic--many-m---", 0], ["af9fa02837db076093a09b6febffefc0-i-cross-the-seven-seas-to---", 0], ["139d950760c7fbd891d9d28d0a920c64-and-we--together--just-li---", 0], ["7b357d96d56e41fb22cd250d0986adde-will-brave-your-trying-ti---", 0], ["a63455380f6bcaf5cbe3fcf4f9d95012-gone--the-day-when-no-one---", 0], ["4a2c957ddac119